'''Maitell Base''' was the primary [[Spaceport/Legends|starport]] on [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]] during the [[Second Galactic Civil War]] fought between the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] and [[Confederation]]. The [[Starship/Legends|starship]] facility also served as a place where visitors could become familiar with the native environment before traveling to [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] [[City/Legends|cities]]. When Kashyyyk was [[Battle of Kashyyyk (Second Galactic Civil War)|attacked]] in [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]] by [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]], the base served as the primary site from which missions were launched to control the forest fires.

